  "texts": [
    "This concludes the proof of (4.3).",
    "Now, for x ∈ H, µ ∈ P 2 (H), and p ∈ H, since H is concave in its last variable, we have",
    "p⟩, for all p ′ ∈ H and any ξ = ξ(x, µ, p) ∈ D + p H(x, µ, p), where D + p H denotes the superdifferential of H in the last variable, see e.g.",
    "[52, Definition E.1].",
    "Let p ′ = p-(1+|p|) ξ |ξ|."
  ],
